<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.188975>
    dc:description "FIGURES 54 – 58. Cuticular structure of females Cunaxa spp. nov.: Cunaxa gordeevae sp. nov. (54); Cunaxa maculate sp. nov. (55, 56); Cunaxa papuliphora sp. nov. (57); Cunaxa violaphila sp. nov. (58)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/188975/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.188970>
    dc:description "FIGURES 27 – 30. Cunaxa papuliphora sp. nov. female. Palp (27); gnathosoma (28): a – venter of hypognathum, b – dorsal aspect; idiosomal dorsum (29); idiosomal venter (30). Scale-bar: 27, 28 — 50 μm; 29, 30 — 100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/188970/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.188971>
    dc:description "FIGURES 31 – 34. Cunaxa papuliphora sp. nov,. female. Genu, tibia and proximal part of tarsus of: leg I (31), leg II (32); genu and tibia of: leg III (33), leg IV (34). Scale-bar— 50 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/188971/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

